      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。标准TCP头部是前160位，那IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic放在160-191位，也就是替代传统的Options字段？后面192-223位留给实际data？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "data",
        "160-191",
        "192-223"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个结构。另外控制位部分要清晰标出URG、ACK、PSH、RST、SYN、FIN这六个标志位，工业场景里ACK和URG的优先级判定很关键。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN",
        "106",
        "107"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出基础框架：0-15位Source Port，16-31位Destination Port，32-63位Sequence Number，64-95位Acknowledgment Number。控制位106-111位依次排开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Acknowledgment的拼写注意一下，是Acknowledgment不是Acknowledgement，工业协议文档里用的是美式拼写。还有Window字段112-127位，Checksum128-143位，Urgent Pointer144-159位，这些都不能漏。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "Window",
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，修正拼写为Acknowledgment。我检查一遍：96-99位Data Offset，100-105位Reserved，然后URG到FIN六个标志位，接着Window、Checksum、Urgent Pointer，最后160-191位放(IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)，192-223位data。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "data"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "结构完整了。特别强调一下，IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic字段用括号标注，表示这是自定义扩展字段，不是标准TCP内容。这样现场工程师一眼就能区分标准头和定制部分。",
